pages.title: About
pages.seo: Everything you wanted to know about us, and were afraid to ask.
pages.body:
Why does this exist when there are literally hundreds of similar starters out there? Easy, I wanted one that I didn't have to doctor up too much to hit the ground running, we all love to get rolling quickly and efficiently right?

Enjoy as is, or head over to [github.com/jackkeller/sveltekit-tailwindcss-netlifycms-typescript](https://github.com/jackkeller/sveltekit-tailwindcss-netlifycms-typescript) so you can fork and edit to fit your needs, you won't hurt my feelings one bit.
pages.keywords: sveltekit, tailwindcss, netlify cms, typescript, coffee and code
